|File:Korea-Seoul-Royal wedding ceremony 1334-06.JPG|王妃赤翟衣
|File:Korea-Hanbok-Queen-02.jpg|朝鮮王朝王妃的绿圆衫
|File:Korea-Hanbok-Queen-01.jpg|织金葡萄吉祥纹凤凰胸背
|File:Seoul-Gyeongbokgung-Chinjamrye-10.jpg|朝鮮王朝[[親蠶禮|親蠶禮]]中[[嬪|嬪]]的圓衫[[禮服|禮服]]
|File:Seoul-Gyeongbokgung-Chinjamrye-05.jpg|親蠶禮穿圓衫的王妃（左）和穿唐衣的尚宮（右）
